            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded mb-3">
            <p>Are you conducting a thorough analysis of all the threads on this forum for academic research or professional advice? We typically include additional minor tasks in the same work order if they can be completed in less than 2 hours. It's important to efficiently manage multiple work orders that require small amounts of manpower. To streamline the change management process, designate a knowledgeable individual to spearhead the implementation of a Computerized Maintenance Management System (CMMS).</p>
